39;微软雅黑&#39;\">爱工作，会生活，懂健康。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">一個可以做火把、</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">点燃自己</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">照亮自己</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">也能带给别人灿烂温暖的人。</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">时间：10月31日周四&nbsp;&nbsp;18:30</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Phase&nbsp;Four&nbsp;&nbsp;C.D.Cafe&nbsp;Leader&nbsp;＆Rookie&nbsp;Salon&nbsp;Activity</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Theme:&nbsp;Share&nbsp;marketing&nbsp;planning&nbsp;experience&nbsp;and&nbsp;entrepreneurial&nbsp;journey&nbsp;with&nbsp;our&nbsp;guest&nbsp;speaker——Weiwei&nbsp;Guan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">There&nbsp;is&nbsp;always&nbsp;one&nbsp;sentence&nbsp;with&nbsp;me:&nbsp;You&nbsp;must&nbsp;struggle&nbsp;hard&nbsp;unconditionally&nbsp;without&nbsp;any&nbsp;complain&nbsp;when&nbsp;you&nbsp;are&nbsp;young.You&nbsp;must&nbsp;fight&nbsp;until&nbsp;