used in the way.</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392791828270580.jpg\" title=\"chuangka.jpg\"/></p>','C.D.Cafe，one of member of China Startup Incubator Alliance.','Resources/uploads/b877db1f5016e29f38921e74817981be.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392709271,1392791839,0),(286,'山东邹平阳光塑复合材料有限公司','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392709361127065.jpg\" title=\"7.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>山东邹平阳光塑复合材料有限公司是民营高科技企业不断追求技术创新,专业技术研发、生产和销售的塑复合和相关的技术咨询和技术服务。产品被欧盟的CE认证,题为“中国优质名牌产品”</p><p>Shandong Zouping Sunlight Wood-Plastic Composites Co., Ltd. is a private high-tech enterprise with constant pursuit of technological innovation, specializing in the technology research and development, production and sales of wood-plastic composite and related technical consulting and technical services.</p><p>The products were certified to the EU’s CE and entitled “China High-quality and Famous Brand Products”&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392790724589180.jpg\" style=\"float:none;\" title=\"eb352dcb-e023-4fb5-8fc4-1f12abeec4fb.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392790725496590.jpg\" style=\"float:none;\" title=\"ee193b53-d6e6-49b9-85fa-9bc027dc0ab2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p>','Shandong Zouping Sunlight Wood-Plastic Composites Co., Ltd.','Resources/uploads/f441b0563d47bc662d543e42e2ea04ab.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392709413,1392790736,0),(287,'《歌舞青春High School Musical》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392710974118543.jpg\" title=\"1.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《歌舞青春High School Musical》</p><p>剧情简介：</p><p><br/></p><p>博尔顿特洛伊和凯碧记得是两个完全不同的青少年在聚会上认识的,在新年前夜唱卡拉ok。一周后特洛伊回到高中时代,他在新墨西哥州东部高,发现加布里埃尔是一个新学生。他们很快成为亲密的朋友,偶试镜为学校音乐剧。在得到一个回调、戏剧皇后夏培埃文斯和她的死党兄弟瑞恩感到愤怒。然后乍得、特洛伊最好的朋友和篮球队友,和泰勒,加布里埃尔的新朋友在十项全能团队,必须找出一种方法,让加布里埃尔讨厌特洛伊<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"></span></p><p><br/></p><p>时间：7月27日周六18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《High School Musical》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>Troy Bolton and Gabriella Montez are two totally different teenagers who meet at a party while singing karaoke on New Year&#39;s Eve. One week later Troy goes back to his high school, East High, in New Mexico to find that Gabriella is a new student there. They quickly become close friends and accidentally audition for the school musical. After getting a callback, drama queen Sharpay Evans and her sidekick brother Ryan are furious. Then Chad, Troy&#39;s best friend and basketball teammate, and Taylor, Gabriella&#39;s new friend on the decathlon team, must find out a way to make Gabriella hate Troy.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:27/07/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392790447118104.jpg\" title=\"1.jpg\"/></p>','《High School Musical》','Resources/uploads/4691637a271ca7c21d5ac940d819dff4.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392711016,1392790471,0),(288,'《牛仔裤的夏天2 The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants 2》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711053126437.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《牛仔裤的夏天2 The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants 2》</p><p>剧情简介：</p><p><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\"></span>卡门·洛厄尔的后台工作在耶鲁大学玩。当女主角和朋友朱莉娅邀请她前往佛蒙特州和她在玩工作专业演员,她决定留在她的朋友和她怀孕的母亲。然而她发现莉娜Kaligaris将前往的绘画。布丽姬特?弗里兰在生存危机失踪的母亲和决定前往土耳其的考古挖掘。蒂Tomko-Rollins还在租金和编辑她的纪录片。因此,卡门接受邀请,前往佛蒙特州。她暗恋男主角伊恩,说服她参加一个试镜,由导演比尔邀请克尔执行导致女性角色。后来她发现真相的友谊茱莉亚。心碎的丽娜发现Kostas刚刚结婚和她约会的模型类。布丽姬特发现信件寄给她和她的祖母,她的父亲已隐藏,她决定去拜访她的奶奶,透露一个秘密对她的母亲。蒂和男朋友做爱布莱恩McBrian但避孕套的问题,她会害怕怀孕的可能性。最后,女友发现,他们的友谊是真实的,超过一条牛仔裤。</p><p>时间：7月31日周三18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>《The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants 2》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Carmen Lowell is working on the backstage of a play in Yale. When the lead actress and friend Julia invites her to travel to Vermont with her to work in a play with professional cast, she decides to stay with her friends and her pregnant mother. However she finds that Lena Kaligaris will travel to a course of drawing. Bridget Vreeland is in existential crisis missing her mother and decides to travel to an archaeological dig in Turkey. Tibby Tomko-Rollins is working in a rental and still editing her documentary. Therefore, Carmen accepts the invitation and travels to Vermont. She has a crush on the lead actor Ian, who convinces her to participate in an audition, and is invited by the director Bill Kerr to perform the lead female role. Later she finds the truth about the friendship of Julia. The broken-hearted Lena finds that Kostas has just married and she dates the model of her class. Bridget finds letters addressed to her from her grandmother that her father has hidden and she decides to visit her grandma, disclosing a secret about her mother. Tibby makes love with her boy-friend Brian McBrian but they have problems with the condom and she gets scared of a possible pregnancy. In the end, the girlfriends discover that their friendship is real and more than a pair of jeans.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:31/07/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392790400980128.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p>','《The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants 2》','Resources/uploads/1b780a148d0875e2ada50fee1480f731.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392711097,1392790409,0),(289,'《初恋50次 First Dates》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711128109244.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《初恋50次 First Dates》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>亨利斯住在夏威夷天堂与公司无休止的女性不带任何附加条件。这是直到他遇见露西惠特莫尔。亨利和露西享受彼此的公司和感觉的开始发生一个严重的关系。第二天接近露西,亨利是困惑当露西无法认出他来。此刻亨利发现露西实际上患有短期记忆丧失和不记得每个人的一天。亨利不会让这阻止他,准备让她再次爱上他,每一天。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：8月3日周六18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《First Dates》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>Henry Roth lives in a Hawaiian paradise with the company of endless women with no strings attached. This is until he meets Lucy Whitmore. Both Henry and Lucy enjoy the company of each other and feel the start of a serious relationship occurring. Approaching Lucy the next day, Henry is confused when Lucy fails to recognize him. This is the moment Henry discovers that Lucy actually suffers from short term memory loss and can&#39;t remember each individual day. Henry won&#39;t let this stop him and is prepared to make her fall in love with him all over again, each and every day.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:03/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392790355994993.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p>','《First Dates》','Resources/uploads/31670028ec2a562f906189a83e7db1ce.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392711161,1392790365,0),(290,'《铁甲钢拳Real Steel》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711188891818.jpg\" title=\"0 (1).jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《铁甲钢拳Real Steel》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>在不久的将来,当人们变得对拳击和类似的运动,创建一个新的运动——机器人拳击在机器人互相战斗,而人所控制。前拳击手查理Kenton,试图使其在新的运动,不仅不做得很好,他非常深红色。当他得知他的前女友,他的母亲的儿子马克斯,死了,他去找出如何处理他。他的前妻的妹妹想在但查理把他第一次说此事。查理问丈夫要钱所以他可以买一个新的机器人,以换取马克斯交给他们。他把马克思的夏天。和Max改善控制他的机器人。但是,当机器人被摧毁,他们去一个废料场部分。麦克斯发现一个老代机器人叫原子和恢复他。马克斯希望原子战斗但查理告诉他他不会最后一轮。然而,原子获胜。也不是很久之前原子越来越大发作。麦克斯让查理教原子如何战斗,和债券strenghtens父亲和儿子。</p><p>时间：8月7日18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Real Steel》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>In the near future when people become uninterested in boxing and similar sports, a new sport is created - Robot boxing wherein robots battle each other while being controlled by someone. Charlie Kenton, a former boxer who&#39;s trying to make it in the new sport, not only doesn&#39;t do well, he is very deeply in the red. When he learns that his ex, mother of his son Max, dies, he goes to figure out what to do with him. His ex&#39;s sister wants to take him in but Charlie has first say in the matter. Charlie asks her husband for money so he can buy a new Robot in exchange for turning Max over to them. He takes Max for the summer. And Max improves his control of his robot. But when the robot is destroyed, they go to a scrap yard to get parts. Max finds an old generation robot named Atom and restores him. Max wants Atom to fight but Charlie tells him he won&#39;t last a round. However, Atom wins. And it isn&#39;t long before Atom is getting major bouts. Max gets Charlie to teach Atom how to fight, and the father and son bond strenghtens.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:07/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392790292726203.jpg\" title=\"0 (1).jpg\"/></p>','《Real Steel》','Resources/uploads/a44a66fbb6285c5211f7cc47cc654683.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392711214,1392790304,0),(291,'《给朱丽叶的信Letters to Juliet》   ','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711245125167.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《给朱丽叶的信Letters to Juliet》 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>一个美国女孩在意大利度假发现一个悬而未决的“写给朱丽叶”——成千上万的信件在虚构的情人维罗纳庭院,通常说的“朱丽叶的秘书”,她接着探索发现恋人在信中引用。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：8月13日18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Letters to Juliet》 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>An American girl on vacation in Italy finds an unanswered &quot;letter to Juliet&quot; -- one of thousands of missives left at the fictional lover&#39;s Verona courtyard, which are typically answered by a the &quot;secretaries of Juliet&quot; -- and she goes on a quest to find the lovers referenced in the letter.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:13/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392790249672077.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p>','《Letters to Juliet》  ','Resources/uploads/d0c17bf901889d93cc5e68676092b43f.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392711273,1392790259,0),(292,'《怦然心动 Flipped》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711316944851.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《怦然心动 Flipped》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>　朱莉·贝克虔诚地相信三件事:树是圣洁的(特别是她最爱的无花果树)、有益于身心健康的鸡蛋她从后院饲养的鸡,收集,有一天她会和布莱斯·罗斯基接吻。自从她看到布莱斯在二年级的产后忧郁症,朱莉·被击杀。不幸的是,布莱斯从未感觉是一样的。坦率地说,他认为朱莉·贝克是有点奇怪——毕竟,什么样的怪胎养鸡和坐在树为了好玩吗?然后,在八年级,一切都变了。布莱斯开始看到朱莉·不同寻常的兴趣和骄傲在她的家人,嗯,挺酷的。和朱莉·开始觉得布莱斯的蓝眼睛一样空布莱斯似乎。毕竟,什么样的混蛋不在乎别人的感受鸡和树木?翻,神秘作家文德林?范Draanen已经从她的萨米凯斯系列,和翻转奇妙的结果。布莱斯和朱莉·咆哮,热情洋溢地谈论彼此的戒指如此真实,青少年读者会快速识别,至少其中的一个搞笑的自我之间无休止的争吵,如果不是两个。一个完美的介绍青少年两性之间的战争。</p><p>时间：8月14日周三18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《 Flipped》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>　　Juli Baker devoutly believes in three things: the sanctity of trees (especially her beloved sycamore), the wholesomeness of the eggs she collects from her backyard flock of chickens, and that someday she will kiss Bryce Loski. Ever since she saw Bryce&#39;s baby blues back in second grade, Juli has been smitten. Unfortunately, Bryce has never felt the same. Frankly, he thinks Juli Baker is a little weird--after all, what kind of freak raises chickens and sits in trees for fun? Then, in eighth grade, everything changes. Bryce begins to see that Juli&#39;s unusual interests and pride in her family are, well, kind of cool. And Juli starts to think that maybe Bryce&#39;s brilliant blue eyes are as empty as the rest of Bryce seems to be. After all, what kind of jerk doesn&#39;t care about other people&#39;s feelings about chickens and trees? With Flipped, mystery author Wendelin Van Draanen has taken a break from her Sammy Keyes series, and the result is flipping fantastic. Bryce and Juli&#39;s rants and raves about each other ring so true that teen readers will quickly identify with at least one of these hilarious feuding egos, if not both. A perfect introduction to the adolescent war between the sexes.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:14/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711348769375.jpg\" title=\"0 (1).jpg\"/></p>','《 Flipped》','Resources/uploads/5b6c57d2f93beb96deb3ef001fbabf1c.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392711352,1392790120,0),(293,'《剪刀手爱德华Edward Scissorhands》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711403127261.jpg\" title=\"0 (2).jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《剪刀手爱德华Edward Scissorhands》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>现代童话,讲述了爱德华,一个人由一个发明家去世之前完成他,用剪刀在他应该双手离开了他。一天,当地的雅芳代表调用历史大厦,他一直独自生活,她需要他回家陪家人。他必须适应新的生活和环境,他不习惯。很快,他展示了一个人才在理发和树篱和赢得了每个人的心。但生活并不总是那么甜。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：8月17日周六18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Edward Scissorhands》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>A modern day fairy tale which tells the story of Edward, a man created by an inventor who died before finishing him and left him with scissors where he should have hands. One day when the local Avon representative calls at the historic mansion where he has been living alone, she takes him home to stay with her family. He has to adapt to the new life and environment that he isn&#39;t used to. Soon he shows a talent in cutting hair and hedges and wins every body&#39;s heart. But life isn&#39;t always so sweet.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:17/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392790084247100.png\" title=\"0.png\"/></p>','《Edward Scissorhands》','Resources/uploads/3d4954d531a6a0bce5008765bf86b292.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392711428,1392790088,0),(294,'《玛丽和马克思 Mary and Max》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711891355961.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《玛丽和马克思 Mary and Max》</p><p>电影简介：</p><p>在1970年代中期,家常,无依无靠的澳大利亚女孩八选一个名字的曼哈顿电话簿和写信给他,她包括一块巧克力。她是玛丽町洋,一个酒鬼母亲的唯一的孩子,父亲是分心。他是马克斯·霍洛维茨,一个超重的人阿斯伯格综合症患者,独自住在纽约。他写道,与巧克力。因此开始了长达20年的信件,留在一个庇护,打断了一些误解。玛丽爱上了邻居,省钱有胎记去除和处理损失。马克斯与邻居的友谊,试图控制自己的体重,终于得到了梦寐以求的工作。这两个会面对面吗?</p><p>时间：8月20日 18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Mary and Max》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>In the mid-1970&#39;s, a homely, friendless Australian girl of 8 picks a name out of a Manhattan phone book and writes to him; she includes a chocolate bar. She&#39;s Mary Dinkle, the only child of an alcoholic mother and a distracted father. He&#39;s Max Horowitz, an overweight man with Asperger&#39;s, living alone in New York. He writes back, with chocolate. Thus begins a 20-year correspondence, interrupted by a stay in an asylum and a few misunderstandings. Mary falls in love with a neighbor, saves money to have a birthmark removed and deals with loss. Max has a friendship with a neighbor, tries to control his weight, and finally gets the dream job. Will the two ever meet face to face?</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:20/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392790036361447.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\"/></p>','《Mary and Max》','Resources/uploads/72c86bc4ea6771717fa57d10478b8cca.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392711900,1392790045,0),(295,'《两小无猜LOVE.ME.IF.YOU.DARE》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711961111212.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《两小无猜LOVE.ME.IF.YOU.DARE》</p><p>剧情简介：</p><p><br/></p><p>朱利安Janvier失去了他的母亲年轻的时候,从他的工人阶级的父亲分开了,曾经接近自信苏菲Kowalsky,波兰类局外人。一个敢游戏,以交换music-box,越来越大胆,无论伤害他人,each-other。在他的大学时代,它甚至暂停他们的关系与他们的婚姻和玩具,但是他们被吸引回到each-other无法抗拒。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：8月21日18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《LOVE.ME.IF.YOU.DARE》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>Julien Janvier lost his mother young, drifted apart from his working class father and ever closer to confident Sophie Kowalsky, the Polish class outsider. Their dares game, symbolized by an interchanged music-box, grows ever bolder, regardless of harm to others and each-other. In his college years, it even suspends their relationship and toys with their marriages, but they are drawn back to each-other irresistibly.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:21/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392711970245650.jpg\" title=\"0 (1).jpg\"/></p>','《LOVE.ME.IF.YOU.DARE》','Resources/uploads/7153cc81481641538cb8f19f6c4cedca.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392711974,1392790001,0),(296,'《老枪Le Vieux Fusil》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712034240087.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《老枪Le Vieux Fusil》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>1944年,母辈朱利安Dandieu是当地医院的外科医生。吓坏了德国军队进入母,他问他的朋友弗朗索瓦?驾驶他的妻子和他的女儿在朱利安的回乡村有一个古老的城堡。一周后,朱利安决定满足然后本周结束,但德国人已经占领了村庄。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：8月22日周四18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Le Vieux Fusil》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>In Montauban in 1944, Julien Dandieu in a surgeon in the local hospital. Frightened by the German army entering Montauban, he asks his friend Francois to drive his wife and his daughter in the back country village where Julien has an old castle. One week later, Julien decided to meet then for the week end, but the Germans are already occupying the village.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:22/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140219/1392789684103858.jpg\" title=\"1.jpg\"/></p>','《Le Vieux Fusil》','Resources/uploads/319b7b4359c98fbbf7186444001fed88.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392712038,1392789771,0),(297,'《美丽人生Life Is Beautiful》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712088210570.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《美丽人生Life Is Beautiful》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>在1930年代的意大利,一个无忧无虑的犹太簿记员名叫Guido开始讨好童话生活,嫁给一个可爱的女人从附近的一个城市。圭多和他的妻子有一个儿子,幸福地生活在一起,直到被德国军队占领意大利。为了保持他的家人在一起,帮助他的儿子生存一个犹太集中营的恐怖,圭多想象大屠杀是一场游戏,获胜的大奖是一辆坦克</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>时间：8月25日周日18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Life Is Beautiful》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>In 1930s Italy, a carefree Jewish book keeper named Guido starts a fairy tale life by courting and marrying a lovely woman from a nearby city. Guido and his wife have a son and live happily together until the occupation of Italy by German forces. In an attempt to hold his family together and help his son survive the horrors of a Jewish Concentration Camp, Guido imagines that the Holocaust is a game and that the grand prize for winning is a tank.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>Time:25/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p>','《Life Is Beautiful》','Resources/uploads/2ee1e33a1ed07e4cc39ee31bd5101ebd.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392712106,1392789620,0),(298,'《追忆奥黛丽赫本Audrey Hepburn Remembered》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712169829404.jpg\" title=\"0 (1).jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《追忆奥黛丽赫本Audrey Hepburn Remembered》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>奥黛丽·赫本是电影最受欢迎的明星之一,拥有美丽,人才,一个优雅的成熟,和一个持久年轻天真的光环。作为联合国儿童基金会的亲善大使,她说世界儿童和家庭的痛苦,获得一个喜爱和崇拜,只会增加她的过早死亡的消息。从明星我们学习她的事业,家庭和友谊,是她优先考虑的事情。导演比利怀尔德,布莱克·爱德华兹,Stanley Donen作曲家亨利·曼奇尼演员格里高利·派克、梅尔·费勒,乔治·邦德和罗杰摩尔,时装设计师纪梵希和其他人来说,加入抢Wolders和肖恩·费雷尔,帮助完成这个爱的肖像。《罗马假日》的片段,塞布丽娜,战争与和平,有趣的脸,蒂凡尼的早餐,伪装,窈窕淑女,两路,罗宾和玛丽安和更多。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：8月26日周一18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Audrey Hepburn Remembered》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>Audrey Hepburn was one of movies best-loved stars, blessed with beauty, talent, an elegant sophistication, and an enduring aura of youthful innocence. As Goodwill Ambassador for UNICEF, she spoke for the world&#39;s suffering children and families, earning an affection and admiration that only increased with news of her untimely death. From the star herself we learn of her career, and the family and friendships that were her priority. Directors Billy Wilder, Blake Edwards and Stanley Donen, composer Henry Mancini, actors Gregory Peck, Mel Ferrer, George Peppard and Roger Moore, fashion designer Hubert de Givenchy and others, join Rob Wolders and Sean Ferrer to help complete this loving portrait. With clips from Roman Holiday, Sabrina, War And Peace, Funny Face, Breakfast At Tiffany&#39;s, Charade, My Fair Lady, Two For the Road, Robin And Marian and more.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>Time:26/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712179101613.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\"/></p>','《Audrey Hepburn Remembered》','Resources/uploads/38f546a6c19900d660d52f92295aeed9.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392712182,1392789572,0),(299,'《海啸奇迹The Impossible》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712254334211.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《海啸奇迹The Impossible》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>普通家庭-玛丽亚(娜奥米·沃茨),亨利(伊万·麦格雷戈)和他们的三个孩子——前往泰国度过圣诞节。他们得到一个升级到海岸线上的别墅。在沉降和交换礼物,他们去游泳池,像很多其他游客。一个完美的度假天堂,直到一个遥远的声音变成了咆哮。没有时间逃离海啸,玛丽亚和她的长子横扫方法之一,亨利和最年轻的。谁将生存,他们将成为什么?</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：8月29日周四18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《The Impossible》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>A regular family - Maria (Naomi Watts), Henry (Ewan McGregor) and their three kids - travel to Thailand to spend Christmas. They get an upgrade to a villa on the coastline. After settling in and exchanging gifts, they go to the pool, like so many other tourists. A perfect paradise vacation until a distant noise becomes a roar. There is no time to escape from the tsunami; Maria and her eldest are swept one way, Henry and the youngest another. Who will survive, and what will become of them?</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:29/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712270581287.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p>','《The Impossible》','Resources/uploads/3eb79bfae3c876d892b3824739486c5f.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392712278,1392789511,0),(300,'《两杆大烟枪Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712334965493.jpg\" title=\"0 (2).jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《两杆大烟枪Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>四个Jack-the-lads发现自己严重——严重严重债务努力一个东区男人和他的执法者弯曲的纸牌游戏。偷听他们的邻居在接下来的平面策划举起一群out-of-their-depth毒品种植,我们的英雄决定缝补强盗。混乱的方式真正开始时,一对古董双重散弹枪失踪在一个完全不同的骗局。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：8月31日周六18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>Four Jack-the-lads find themselves heavily - seriously heavily - in debt to an East End hard man and his enforcers after a crooked card game. Overhearing their neighbours in the next flat plotting to hold up a group of out-of-their-depth drug growers, our heros decide to stitch up the robbers in turn. In a way the confusion really starts when a pair of antique double-barrelled shotguns go missing in a completely different scam.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:31/08/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712351133597.png\" title=\"0.png\"/></p>','《Lock, Stock and Two Smoking Barrels》','Resources/uploads/7ed5dd6987f95bebe0fe882e00323ff8.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392712355,1392789442,0),(301,'《怪兽大学Monsters University》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712423404504.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《怪兽大学Monsters University》</p><p><br/></p><p>剧情简介：</p><p>迈克Wazowski和詹姆斯·p·沙利文是一对不可分割的,但这并非总是如此。从这两个不匹配的怪物他们无法忍受彼此相遇。“怪兽大学”打开门迈克和苏利克服分歧,如何成为最好的朋友。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：9月1日周日18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Monsters University》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>Mike Wazowski and James P. Sullivan are an inseparable pair, but that wasn&#39;t always the case. From the moment these two mismatched monsters met they couldn&#39;t stand each other. &quot;Monsters University&quot; unlocks the door to how Mike and Sulley overcame their differences and became the best of friends.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:01/09/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712433122770.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p>','《Monsters University》','Resources/uploads/b2df7cbcf1ce1ae0f10aeb622c91ce7a.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392712436,1392789385,0),(302,'《辛德勒的名单Schindler\'s List》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712495353697.jpg\" title=\"0.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《辛德勒的名单Schindler&#39;s List》</p><p>剧情简介：</p><p><br/></p><p>捷克出生的奥斯卡·辛德勒的真实故事,一个商人试图使他的财富在第二次世界大战期间,利用犹太人的廉价劳动力,但最终身无分文保存超过1000波兰犹太人在大屠杀中几乎必死无疑。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：9月2日周一18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Schindler&#39;s List》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>The true story of Czech born Oskar Schindler, a businessman who tried to make his fortune during the Second World War by exploiting cheap Jewish labour, but ended up penniless having saved over 1000 Polish Jews from almost certain death during the holocaust.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:02/09/2013 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712509108217.jpg\" title=\"0 (1).jpg\"/></p>','《Schindler\'s List》','Resources/uploads/10740a92763ee220f2fac28003d81541.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392712511,1392789310,0),(303,'《蒂凡尼的早餐 Breakfast at Tiffany\'s》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712824784528.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《蒂凡尼的早餐 Breakfast at Tiffany&#39;s》</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;剧情简介：</p><p>霍莉(奥黛丽·赫本)生活在曼哈顿的斯万克东区上流社会的。完全鲁莽的人,她有一个部分有家具的公寓,拥有一只猫没有名字,摆脱“心绪不宁”的访问蒂凡尼珠宝店,和永远遗忘她的门钥匙,失望的是她楼上的邻居Yunioshi先生(米奇鲁尼),一个日本摄影师。冬青使她生活在两个方面:她从绅士获得50美元护送每当她需要盥洗室钱,和她为每个每周旅行支付了100美元对新新监狱,在那里她访问莎莉番茄(ALAN REED),一个ex-mobster。一天,保罗Varjak(乔治·邦德),一个年轻的作家,是由一个老女人的绰号“2 e”(帕特里夏尼尔),进入冬青的生活。冬青的野生后举办的鸡尾酒会她的好莱坞经纪人,O.J.伯曼(MARTIN香脂),保罗意外满足医生戈莱特利(BUDDY EBSEN),温柔的德克萨斯冬青娶她只有15岁。冬青解释保罗,婚姻被宣告无效很久以前,他帮助她把伤心的医生。经过一天一起在城里,保罗意识到自己爱上了冬青和建议她,但她决心嫁给穆(VILALLONGA),南美百万富翁。然而,当它是公开透露,冬青一直天真地携带毒品从莎莉番茄环信息他纽约associates闷穆抛弃了她。一切,每个人都火冒三丈,冬青踢猫从她的出租车到雨和决定离开巴西,但保罗讲座她,然后出去找猫。冬青实现多少她放弃和种族穿过潮湿的纽约街道与保罗和猫一个快乐的聚会。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：1月03日周五18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《 Breakfast at Tiffany&#39;s》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>Holly Golightly (AUDREY HEPBURN) lives in a brownstone on Manhattan&#39;s swank East Side. Totally madcap, she has a partially furnished apartment, owns a cat with no name, gets rid of the &quot;mean reds&quot; by visiting Tiffany&#39;s jewelry store, and is forever misplacing her door key, much to the dismay of her upstairs neighbor Mr. Yunioshi (MICKEY ROONEY), a Japanese photographer. Holly makes her living in two ways: she receive $50 from her gentlemen escorts whenever she needs powder room money, and she is paid $100 for each weekly trip she makes to Sing Sing Prison, where she visits Sally Tomato (ALAN REED), an ex-mobster. One day Paul Varjak (GEORGE PEPPARD), a young writer who is supported by an older woman nicknamed &quot;2E&quot; (PATRICIA NEAL), comes into Holly&#39;s life. Following one of Holly&#39;s wild cocktail parties hosted by her Hollywood agent, O.J. Berman (MARTIN BALSAM), Paul unexpectedly meets Doc Golightly (BUDDY EBSEN), a gentle Texan whom Holly married when she was only 15 years old. Holly explains to Paul that the marriage was annulled long ago, and he helps her send the heartbroken Doc away. After a day on the town together, Paul realizes that he is in love with Holly and proposes to her; but she is determined to marry José (VILALLONGA), a South American millionaire. However, when it is publicly revealed that Holly has been innocently carrying narcotics ring information from Sally Tomato to his New York associates, the stuffy José abandons her. Furious at everything and everyone, Holly kicks Cat out of her taxicab into the rain and decides to leave town for Brazil, but Paul lectures her and then goes out to find Cat. Holly realizes how much she is giving up and races through the wet New York streets to a happy reunion with Paul and Cat.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:03/01/2014 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712836426743.jpg\" title=\"4.jpg\"/></p>','《 Breakfast at Tiffany\'s》','Resources/uploads/256c84ebec058d152f38682f2b6e2dd9.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392712840,1392789954,0),(304,'《音乐会 Le concert》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712881485100.jpg\" title=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《音乐会 Le concert》</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;剧情简介：</p><p>三十年前,安德烈Simoniovich波包间管弦乐队的著名指挥家,招聘犹太音乐家被解雇了。现在只有清洁人包间,他偶然得知,在巴黎的小城堡剧院邀请包间管弦乐队演奏。他决定聚集在巴黎他以前的音乐家和执行当前包间的管弦乐队的地方。小提琴独奏播放器陪他老犹太或吉普赛的音乐家,他希望安妮Jacquet,一个年轻的艺术大师。如果他们都克服前面的困难这个非常特别的音乐会将是一个胜利。</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：1月06日周一18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《 Le concert》</p><p><br/></p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>Thirty years ago, Andrei Simoniovich Filipov, the renowned conductor of the Bolshoi orchestra, was fired for hiring Jewish musicians. Now a mere cleaning man at the Bolshoi, he learns by accident that the Chatelet Theater in Paris invites the Bolshoi orchestra to play there. He decides to gather together his former musicians and to perform in Paris in the place of the current Bolshoi orchestra. As a solo violin player to accompany his old Jewish or Gypsy musicians he wants Anne-Marie Jacquet, a young virtuoso. If they all overcome the hardships ahead this very special concert will be a triumph.</p><p><br/></p><p>Time:06/01/2014 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712894226216.jpg\" title=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712906185059.jpg\" title=\"5 (1).jpg\"/></p>','《 Le concert》','Resources/uploads/f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392712909,1392713107,0),(305,'《天堂电影院 Nuovo Cinema Paradiso (1988)》','<p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392712994122961.jpg\" title=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p>《天堂电影院 Nuovo Cinema Paradiso (1988)》</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;剧情简介：</p><p><br/></p><p>一个男孩成长于一个本地西西里村回家作为著名导演收到消息后死亡的一个老朋友。告诉在闪回中,塞尔瓦托与阿尔弗雷多回忆他的童年和他的关系,在天堂电影院放映员。阿尔弗雷多的父亲的影响下,萨尔瓦多爱上了电影制作,与两人花很多时间讨论电影和阿尔弗雷多精心教学萨尔瓦多的技能成为垫脚石的小男孩成为世界电影制作。这部电影使观众通过电影和传统电影的垂死的贸易的变化,编辑和筛选。它还探讨了一个小男孩的梦想离开他的小镇进军外面的世界.</p><p><br/></p><p>时间：1月07日周二18:00</p><p>地址：济南大学七教西段国际教育交流学院副楼一层C.D.Cafe</p><p><br/></p><p>《Nuovo Cinema Paradiso (1988)》</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>Introduction:&nbsp;</p><p>A boy who grew up in a native Sicilian Village returns home as a famous director after receiving news about the death of an old friend. Told in a flashback, Salvatore reminiscences about his childhood and his relationship with Alfredo, a projectionist at Cinema Paradiso. Under the fatherly influence of Alfredo, Salvatore fell in love with film making, with the duo spending many hours discussing about films and Alfredo painstakingly teaching Salvatore the skills that became a stepping stone for the young boy into the world of film making. The film brings the audience through the changes in cinema and the dying trade of traditional film making, editing and screening. It also explores a young boy&#39;s dream of leaving his little town to foray into the world outside.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Time:07/01/2014 &nbsp; 18:00</p><p><br/></p><p>Address: C.D.Cafe,The first floor in the west of the NO.7 Building (the vice Building of College of International Education Exchange) ,University of Jinan</p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392713007123576.jpg\" title=\"4.jpg\"/></p><p><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392713018341592.jpg\" title=\"5.jpg\"/></p>','《Nuovo Cinema Paradiso (1988)》','Resources/uploads/cfde5a962fe53c0b10c08bf469c8c0b2.jpg','admin',NULL,1,0,1392713036,1392787408,0),(306,'影像茶话会：还原一个我们所不知道的数字影院','<p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\"><img src=\"http://cdcafe.cc/Common/libs/ueditor/../../../Resources/uploads//20140218/1392714772831449.jpg\" title=\"eca86bd9dc5f141ef4e40c.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">影像茶话会：还原一个我们所不知道的数字影院</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">茶聊背景：</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;数字影院的大发展，对院线来说既是机遇，也是挑战</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2013<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">月，阿方索·卡隆执导的《地心引力》在北美地区上映，因其强大而令人叹为观止的技术特效，在极短时间内便在全世界范围掀起了继《阿凡达》后最为汹涌的数字观影狂潮。当亿万观众坐在</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3D</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">IMAX</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">巨幕下，身临其境地进入影片所刻画的太空空间并为数字技术惊叹时，数字电影走过了急速发展的十余年，中国电影市场也完成了全方位蜕变。</span></span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px\"><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">关于数字电影与数字影院，你究竟了解多少？冲一壶咖啡，闲谈一下进行求解、整理，还原一个我们所不知道的数字影院。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:37px\"><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">茶话会主题：</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">还原一个我们所不知道的数字影院</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">茶话会话题：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、数字电影是什么</span></span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、影院如何拿到影片</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">3、</span><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\">观影为啥吃爆米花</span></p><p><span style=\";font-size:19px;font-family:&#39;宋体&#39;\